Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haru-chan, good morning~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're experimenting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were talking about how much our skirts\Nwould move when we're actually dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if it was Producer who came in instead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We almost got him locked up in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:03:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, man, how can idols\Ndance around in those frilly outfits?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're an idol too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember ever becoming one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think a cute outfit\Nwould really fit you, Haru-chan~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can recall ever\Nseeing you in one, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! You've got a nice body, Haru,\Nso you should wear skirts and stuff like that more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like wearing these kinds of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, fashion is about how you match clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we just get you a matching bottom... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are Yuuki-san and Matoba-san here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that any way to enter a room\Nwhere ladies are present?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is where I work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, where's Yuuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm? Do you need me for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! And Matoba-san too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you two want to try being backup dancers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Backup dancers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the girls who were\Noriginally picked for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...had other commitments come up\Nthat they couldn't miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A live concert? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-p...P?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's LiPPS! I told you about them earlier, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's actually happening this weekend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a really short amount of time to practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there are a lot of events\Nin the summer, so everyone is busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was hard to find people\Nwhose schedules matched...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But considering how Yuuki-san's so athletic,\Nand how Matoba-san's a fast learner,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt like they could handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, they certainly\Nare the best choice for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're both excellent at dancing, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what I hoped, Matoba-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you, Yuuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:05:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I don't really get this whole idol thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but this seems pretty cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like playing defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, backup dancers are cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're an irreplaceable\Npart of the performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that bring more impact by\Nadding more movement to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's an important job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assists are important, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soccer-for-brains...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright then, I'll do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wahh~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall be cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, then let's start the lessons right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup, you're looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's so easy to read, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Risa, your tempo\Nwas off by a beat earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, your movements are sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's run through it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.81,Sign Generic,,0,0,0,,{\fs9\blur1.25\frz343\pos(1084,733)}Lazy Lazy – Crazy Crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... Ichinose Shiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, it's Ichinose Shi–
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spot on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nyahaha~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been watching since\Nyour first day of lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Then you should've said... something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff, sniff, sniff...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smell, smell, smell, smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff, sniff...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your dancing seems fine,\Nso Shiki-chan's leaving now~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh right,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm actually really looking forward to this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you don't entertain me, I might use you\Nas guinea pigs for some sketchy drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nyahahaha~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that, what was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idols are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not everyone is like Shiki, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your outfits have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take your detailed measurements,\Nso can you wear them during practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, no way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with these clothes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not wearin' them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-some people don't like cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a good opportunity to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll definitely look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-hey, isn't there some way\Nwe can change the outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're made to match LiPPS's, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yuuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I definitely thought you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you want to wear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Umm... Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's girly, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mmh... Listen, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The performance is soon, so this\Nisn't the time to start being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You decided you were going to do it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving up halfway is the lamest thing possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I didn't know\Nabout this when I agreed to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had known from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Now, now, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, being an idol isn't so laid-back\Nthat you can be picky about your outfits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm always telling you that you need to be\Nmore aware of the fact that you're an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get it through your head already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this 'cause I wanted\Nto be an idol like you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go cool off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wai– Yuuki-san!
