Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh, god, this sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up and chase after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? But, Matoba-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haru would definitely be at that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuki-sa–
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Producer!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came to the agency 'cause your\Nfamily told you to, right, Yuuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My old man was saying\Nhe wanted me to dress cuter and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to play soccer over the summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but even my brothers thought it'd be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like I hate everything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, I still like soccer the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I like getting to move my body,\Nand dancing is like working on a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true. You two were amazing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She can be harsh with her words,\Nbut she's super serious about being an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if I'm doing it, I wanna take it seriously too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But suddenly having to wear that outfit\Nis just so hard, and there's no time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so bad at thinking through all this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone on your team wasn't taking it\Nseriously, of course that'd piss you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so fun about being an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well that's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah...
