Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go see together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yuuki-san, Matoba-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's start our screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this, Producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Yuuki-san, have\Nyou ever seen an idol concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen music programs and stuff before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-well anyway, try watching just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you do, I'm sure, {\i1}sure{\i0}\Nthat you'll come to like idols.
