Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At soccer matches, it's so much fun\Ncheering along with everyone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... actually playing is tons\Nmore fun than just watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If being an idol is the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then it might not be so bad\Nto try and stand up there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, are you gonna be okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh right, the outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the one that said if we left it to\Nyour kids, they'd definitely be fine, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what's this about, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I understand that it would be difficult, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I'm sure she'd be able to give\Na much better performance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be dealing with\Nthat kind of selfishness on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Selfishness"? They're still just ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the time being, I'll ask the higher-ups,\Nbut don't get your hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine since you'd look good in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm saying that's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To start with, I never agreed to wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, why a skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get them to change the outfit, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why... I figured this was just\Nabout the only thing left that I could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you move like that, it's even grosser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't call me gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're very cute, Producer-san~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apologize to Sasaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, A-Arisu-chan, Chie's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pfft...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure looks good on you, Producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong with being selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I mean, even just the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuki-san, Matoba-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think you're ready to start the lesson?
