Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haru-chan, you did wonderfully~
